            is_pot(pot) and id[pot]==2069

def has_vegetable_near_pot(pot:item):
    # Function to check if there is a vegetable near the pot
    symbol vegetable_near_pot=exists o: item : is_food_vegetable(o) and close_char(char, pot)
    return vegetable_near_pot

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind pot: item where:
            is_pot(pot) and close_char(char, pot)
        # Select a pot that is near the character

        if has_vegetable_near_pot(pot):
            bind vegetable: item where:
                is_food_vegetable(vegetable) and close_char(char, pot)
            # Select a vegetable that is near the pot
            achieve inside(vegetable, pot)
            # Place the vegetable inside the pot
        
        else:
            bind fridge: item where:
                is_fridge(fridge) and close_char(char, fridge)

            observe(fridge, "Check for food_vegetable inside the fridge")

            bind vegetable: item where:
                is_food_vegetable(vegetable) and close_char(char, fridge)
            # Select vegetable near the fridge
            achieve close_char(char, pot)
            # Move back to the pot
            achieve inside(vegetable, pot)
            # Put the vegetable inside the pot

def has_vegetable_nearby_counter(counter:item):
    # Function to check if there are vegetables near the kitchen counter
    symbol has_vegetable=exists o: item : is_food_vegetable(o) and close(o, counter)
    return has_vegetable

    body:
        achieve inside(vegetable, pot) # Place the vegetable inside the pot

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind counter: item where:
            is_kitchen_counter(counter)
        # Select a kitchen counter
